    <string name="about_privacy_body">This app prioritizes your privacy. All financial data (transactions, balances, and history) is stored locally on your device using an encrypted database.\n\n1. Notification Processing:\nNotifications are processed locally on-device. Only relevant text content required for transaction analysis is sent to AI.\n\n2. User-Controlled Storage:\nNo personal financial data is stored on our servers. Data resides locally on your device or securely in your personal Google Drive. We have no access to your data.\n\n3. AI Assistance:\nAI is used solely as a supportive tool for transaction detection and classification. Personalization rules remain stored on-device.</string>
    <string name="about_desc">Design &amp; Integration by\n白开水 (Bai Kai Shui)\n\nAI-Assisted Code Generation\nPowered by Google Gemini\n\nData Transparency &amp; Privacy\nThis app prioritizes your privacy. All financial data is stored locally. No cloud servers.</string>
